whole_object: When I told my friends I had a yacht, they thought I was being boastful, but clearly, I'm just ship-shape in telling the truth.
single_object:
- Sink: This sink might be in hot water for always being drained at parties!
- Stove: The stove's favorite band must be 'The Flaming Lips' because it's always cooking up hits.
- Table: This table stands four legs above competition when it comes to holding things up.
- Benches: These benches are outstanding in their field—of seating!
- Cabinets: These cabinets are so good at hiding things; they're practically in the witness protection program.
- Windows: These windows are clearly the best at transparency.
- Map: This map might just be the center of attention, leading everyone in the right direction.
- Control panel: The control panel is buttoned up, always pressed for information.
- Cushions: Cushions are the unsung heroes; they've got your back, quietly.
- Skylight: The skylight's career is definitely on the up and up, it's a true rising star.
